msgstr "`v0.1.0` - Introduced."

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:55
msgid ""
"`ptool.semver.bump(v, op[, channel])` returns a new version object after "
"applying the bump."
msgstr "`ptool.semver.bump(v, op[, channel])` は、更新を適用した新しい バージョンオブ"
"ジェクトを返します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:58
msgid "`v` (string|Version, required): The original version."
msgstr "`v` (string|Version, 必須): 元のバージョン。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:59
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:59"
msgid ""
"`op` (string, required): One of `major`, `minor`, `patch`, `release`, `alpha`"
", `beta`, `rc`, `prepatch`, `preminor`, or `premajor`."
msgstr ""
"`op` (string, 必須): `major`, `minor`, `patch`, `release`, `alpha`, `beta`, "
"`rc`, `prepatch`, `preminor`, `premajor` のいずれか。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:61
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:61"
msgid ""
"`channel` (string, optional): Supported only for `prepatch`, `preminor`, and "
"`premajor`. Must be one of `alpha`, `beta`, or `rc`. Defaults to `alpha`."
msgstr ""
"`channel` (string, 任意): `prepatch`, `preminor`, `premajor` でのみ 使用でき"
"ます。`alpha`, `beta`, `rc` のいずれかで、デフォルトは `alpha` です。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:63
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/semver.md:63"
msgid "Returns: `Version`."
msgstr "戻り値: `Version`."

